title: Naive Set "Let Me Down" - Converse Red Light Sessions
description: On 8th March Dutch indie pop band Naïve Set kicked off the 2014 series of Converse Red Light Sessions, giving local talent the opportunity to play alongside international talent coming through Amsterdam, Naïve Set were up with psychedelic hip hop trio Young Fathers.
